headline: Best Stock to Buy Right Now: Walmart vs. Costco
summary: Costco will appeal to more growth-focused investors, while Walmart delivers higher profits.  Owning Costco (NASDAQ: COST) or Walmart (NYSE: WMT) stock today might seem risky, given the uncertainty around tariffs and economic growth.
